Package: cm4all-state
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Tool for managing CM4all state directories
 State directories are a set of directories where the desired state of
 software components is stored.
 .
 This package contains a command-line tool for managing them.

